Scenario: champions_room_victory_to_hall_of_fame
Description: Run the Champions Room post-battle script and verify it completes the room and warps to Hall of Fame entry.
Character: ScriptSimChampionRoomVictory

Initial state
  location: CHAMPIONS_ROOM[120] (4,3)
  flags: EVENT_BEAT_CHAMPION_RIVAL, EVENT_GOT_POKEDEX, EVENT_PLAYER_CHOSE_CHARMANDER
  party:
